tansMNIST: apply one customized transformation to one digit
operation vector: 4 dim one-hot vactors -> 100 dim rep instead of one a random numver between 4-8 specifying the transformation

two entities: image and operation
choose rule with attention rule-entites (we want it to choose from operation entity)
apply rule to image entity after concating the number specifying the transformation

NPS manage to distinguish the four rules and make rules that canbe adjusted with a number

